==命名==
虽然没有[[愛德華·德林克·科普|愛德華·德林克·科普]]的原始描述证实，但在希腊语中，凶齿豨学名的意思是"凶残的牙齿"<ref name="#1"/>。

== 描述 ==

凶齒豨是目前已知最大型的[[豨科|豨科]]<ref name="lucasetal1997">{{cite journal | last1 = Lucas | first1 = S.G. | last2 = Emry | first2 = R.J. | last3 = Foss | first3 = S.E. | year = 1998 | title = Taxonomy and distribution of ''Daeodon'', an Oligocene-Miocene entelodont (Mammalia: Artiodactyla) from North America | url = https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/48793 | journal = Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington | volume = 111 | issue = 2 | pages = 425–435 | access-date = 2018-10-16 | archive-date = 2018-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181016125929/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/48793 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，目前已知成年顱骨長度可達 {{Convert|90|cm|ft|abbr = on|sigfig = 1}}，肩高則可達 {{Convert|1.77|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref name="Peterson1909">{{cite journal|last=Peterson|first=O. A.|title=A revision of the Entelodontidae|journal=Memoirs of the Carnegie Museum|year=1909|volume=4|issue=3|pages=41–158|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/bibliography/46733#/summary|access-date=2018-10-16|archive-date=2018-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016125934/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/bibliography/46733#/summary|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凶齒豨的頸骨並不特別粗壯，其頭顱的重量主要是透過連結至[[胸椎|胸椎]]高聳棘突的肌肉與肌腱來支撐，類似現存的[[美洲野牛|美洲野牛]]以及[[白犀牛|白犀牛]]<ref name="Effinger1998">{{cite book|last=Effinger|first=J. A.|title=Evolution of Tertiary Mammals of North America. Volume 1: Terrestrial Carnivores, Ungulates, and Ungulatelike Mammals.|year=1998|publisher=Cambridge University Press|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/Evolution_of_Tertiary_Mammals_of_North_A.html?id=I-RgojcDyWYC|editor=Janis, C. M.|editor2=Scott, K. M.|editor3=Jacobs, L. L.|chapter=Entelodontidae|access-date=2018-10-16|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829133041/https://books.google.com/books/about/Evolution_of_Tertiary_Mammals_of_North_A.html%3Fid%3DI-RgojcDyWYC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

